President Muhammadu Buhari has approved a new official portrait for display in all Public Offices, buildings and for other legitimate purposes. In this regard, all Ministries, Departments, Agencies of Government, Sub-National Entities, Businesses and the Public are enjoined to obtain soft copy of the portrait from either of the following two Offices: “Office of the Permanent Secretary, Federal Ministry of Information and Culture Radio House, Garki, Abuja. “Office of the Director (Information) Office of the Secretary to the Government of the Federation, Shehu Shagari Complex, Three Arms Zone Abuja. A statement by Olusegun Adekunle, who is the Permanent Secretary General Services Office  in the office of the SGF, said that sample copy of the new official portrait can be viewed and downloaded on the official website of the Office of the Secretary to the Government of the Federation on www.osgf.gov.ng.